thread.title: Caroline Clohesy
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Caroline Clohesy

author: Caroline Clohesy
title: Caroline Clohesy
text:
I was super impressed with the range and quality of toner that Inkstation have on board. It feels ridiculous these days that I could literally go out an by a new printer for the price of some toners. What the manufacturers never tell you though is that the timer they supply is never a fun toner!
This is a great place for laser or inkkject toner supply.
I'll be using them again for sure!
